  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"6fzMTLV1\">建议在下次怀孕前到生殖门诊咨询，夫妻双方孕前检查，包括染色体检查。</p><p data-pid=\"r8gMkfyE\">下一胎怀孕后孕期需要做产前诊断，即<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=532939455&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%BB%92%E6%AF%9B%E6%9F%93%E8%89%B2%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">绒毛染色体检查<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>或羊水穿刺进行产前诊断，确定胎儿是否存在染色体异常。</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
  "excerpt": "建议在下次怀孕前到生殖门诊咨询，夫妻双方孕前检查，包括染色体检查。\n\n下一胎怀孕后孕期需要做产前诊断，即绒毛染色体检查或羊水穿刺进行产前诊断，确定胎儿是否存在染色体异常。",
